---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Der Town"
  description="Learn about Der Town, a community platform connecting neighbors through local events, activities, and announcements in Leavenworth, Washington."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-95 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-2xl w-full p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About Der Town</h1>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-800">
        This page is here for the benefit of our community in Leavenworth, Washington and is maintained by a local resident who found it hard to keep track of what was going on.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-800">
        Please let us know if you would like to make any requested changes, would like to help out, or have another good source of content that should be added.
      </p>
      <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg border border-indigo-100">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-800 mb-2">Manage your organization's events</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-800">
          We're beginning to experiment with admin accounts for local organizations and venues to manage and curate their own events on Dertown. If you represent an organization in the Leavenworth area and are interested, email us at <a href="mailto:dertownleavenworth@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 underline hover:text-indigo-800">dertownleavenworth@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-700">See ya out there!</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 